OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fbright evening with some hazy sunny
OL,7,Fspells. For Orkney the rest of the
OL,8,Fnight will remain dry with clear
OL,9,Fspells. Chance of the odd light shower
OL,10,Ffor Shetland. Gentle to moderate
OL,11,Fwesterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA dry and bright day with
OL,14,Fsome sunshine, albeit often rather
OL,15,Fhazy. Chance of the odd light shower
OL,16,Ffor Shetland in the morning. Mainly
OL,17,Fgentle winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
